data.description: Immaculate  MOVE-IN READY  FURNISHED  3/2/2 SPLIT FLOORPLAN NORTH PORT HOME. Conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, medical facilities, 4 airports, I-75, sports arenas, world class beaches and so much more! Home is well maintained with many added features.  Vaulted ceilings and art niches add architectural interest. Many updates to the home have been made such as a new roof 2020, HVAC 2019,  Whole House Reverse Osmosis System for clean, clear drinking and bathing water by Aquaflow.  Solid flooring throughout the home makes cleaning floors a breeze. Newly added floating luxury vinyl plank flooring in all bedrooms and ceramic tile everywhere else is an added feature. The master bedroom ensuite has a soaking tub and a separate glass-enclosed shower. Kitchen has a new refrigerator (2022) and a moveable island for added counter space and storage. The laundry room features the LG SMART Washer & Dryer System. Furniture Available.  The nice-sized backyard allows room for a pool.  A 10X12 shed has electricity and plenty of room for hurricane shutters, bikes, tools and more under lock and key.  This charming home has it all!  Make your appointment today.
